    "assignee": null,
    "body": "For some reason, connection time is horrendously slow (between 8-10 seconds), even with native URSA. There are multiple sources of slowness :\r\n\r\n- The DNS lookup may take up to 4 seconds on my machine to fail to resolve\r\n- The requests to mojang may take up to 2-3 seconds each\r\n- The js RSA implementation is slow (fixed by using URSA, sorta).\r\n- Sometimes generating random numbers can be slow.\r\n\r\nWe should profile the login time of node-minecraft-protocol to identify and fix the potential bottlenecks.",
    "closed_at": "2015-05-21T12:58:26Z",
